Mauritius Plans ‘Rainy Day Fund’ in 2012 Budget, Le Defi Says

-- B y   K a m l e s h   B h u c k o r y
-- 
2011-10-06T08:14:31Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-06/mauritius-plans-rainy-day-fund-in-2012-budget-le-defi-says.html
Mauritius’s Finance Minister Xavier Luc Duval plans to announce the creation of a “Rainy Day Fund”
in his budget speech for 2012, Le Defi Quotidien reported,
citing the minister.  The fund will aim to help strategic segments of the
economy, and support employment and growth, the Port Louis-based
newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
